Title: Westward Bound
Description:
Captain Garrick wants us tae search west o' camp fer any other members of the expedition.

Alaria and I will go on ahead. Meet us tae the west and we'll see what we can find.
ObjectivesText: Meet Bjorn Stouthands west of the Alliance Camp.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Bjorn Stouthands west of the Alliance Camp.
RewardText: A giant pit of spiders right on our doorstep! Aren't we the lucky ones?
